headline: FuriosaAI Unveils Enterprise-Ready NXT RNGD Server As Global Demand For Energy-Efficient AI Inference Surges Beyond Traditional GPU Systems
summary: FuriosaAI's newly launched NXT RNGD server could change the economics of enterprise AI deployments, delivering high-performance inference while using far less energy than the market's most expensive GPU systems, according to the company. Global power demand from data centers is projected to climb 50% by 2027 and as much as 165% by 2030, driven largely by artificial intelligence workloads, according to Goldman Sachs (NYSE: GS).
